        "liquid": "<style>\n@import url('https://fonts.cdnfonts.com/css/neue-montreal');\n\n.reasons-section {\n  width: 100vw;\n  margin-left: calc(50% - 50vw);\n  background: linear-gradient(180deg, #DCF0FD 0%, #fff 100%);\n  padding: 100px 20px;\n}\n\n.reasons-container {\n  max-width: 1100px;\n  margin: 0 auto;\n  display: grid;\n  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\n  gap: 80px;\n  align-items: start;\n}\n\n/* GAUCHE */\n.reasons-left {\n  position: sticky;\n  top: 100px;\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: column;\n  align-items: center;\n  gap: 36px;\n}\n\n.reasons-eyebrow {\n  font-family: 'Neue Montreal', 'Inter', sans-serif;\n  font-size: 10px;\n  font-weight: 500;\n  letter-spacing: 3px;\n  text-transform: uppercase;\n  color: #888;\n  text-align: center;\n}\n\n.reasons-title {\n  font-family: 'Neue Montreal', 'Inter', sans-serif;\n  font-size: 32px;\n  font-weight: 300;\n  line-height: 1.2;\n  color: #000;\n  letter-spacing: -1px;\n  text-align: center;\n}\n\n.reasons-title em {\n  font-style: italic;\n}\n\n.video-circle {\n  width: 300px;\n  height: 300px;\n  border-radius: 50%;\n  overflow: hidden;\n  background: #000;\n  box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);\n  -webkit-transform: translateZ(0);\n  transform: translateZ(0);\n  -webkit-backface-visibility: hidden;\n  backface-visibility: hidden;\n  will-change: transform;\n}\n\n.video-circle video,\n.video-circle img {\n  width: 100%;\n  height: 100%;\n  object-fit: cover;\n  border-radius: 50%;\n  display: block;\n  -webkit-mask-image: -webkit-radial-gradient(circle, white 100%, black 100%);\n  mask-image: radial-gradient(circle, white 100%, black 100%);\n}\n\n.video-circle video::-webkit-media-controls,\n.video-circle video::-webkit-media-controls-enclosure,\n.video-circle video::-webkit-media-controls-panel,\n.video-circle video::-webkit-media-controls-play-button,\n.video-circle video::-webkit-media-controls-start-playback-button {\n  display: none !important;\n}\n\n.video-circle .mobile-gif { display: none; }\n\n@media (max-width: 968px) {\n  .video-circle video { display: none; }\n  .video-circle .mobile-gif { display: block; }\n}\n\n/* DROITE */\n.reasons-right {\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: column;\n  gap: 0;\n}\n\n.reason-item {\n  display: flex;\n  gap: 24px;\n  align-items: flex-start;\n  padding: 32px 0;\n  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08);\n  transition: background 0.2s ease;\n}\n\n.reason-item:first-child {\n  padding-top: 0;\n}\n\n.reason-item:last-child {\n  border-bottom: none;\n  padding-bottom: 0;\n}\n\n.reason-circle {\n  width: 88px;\n  height: 88px;\n  min-width: 88px;\n  border-radius: 50%;\n  overflow: hidden;\n  background: #fff;\n  box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.07);\n  -webkit-transform: translateZ(0);\n  transform: translateZ(0);\n  flex-shrink: 0;\n}\n\n.reason-circle img {\n  width: 100%;\n  height: 100%;\n  object-fit: cover;\n  display: block;\n}\n\n.reason-number {\n  font-family: 'Neue Montreal', 'Inter', sans-serif;\n  font-size: 10px;\n  font-weight: 500;\n  letter-spacing: 2px;\n  text-transform: uppercase;\n  color: #aaa;\n  margin-bottom: 8px;\n}\n\n.reason-content h3 {\n  font-family: 'Neue Montreal', 'Inter', sans-serif;\n  font-size: 17px;\n  font-weight: 600;\n  margin-bottom: 10px;\n  color: #000;\n  line-height: 1.3;\n  letter-spacing: -0.3px;\n}\n\n.reason-content p {\n  font-family: 'Neue Montreal', 'Inter', sans-serif;\n  font-size: 14px;\n  line-height: 1.75;\n  color: #666;\n  font-weight: 300;\n  margin: 0;\n}\n\n/* RESPONSIVE */\n@media (max-width: 968px) {\n  .reasons-container {\n    grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n    gap: 50px;\n  }\n  .reasons-left {\n    position: relative;\n    top: 0;\n  }\n  .video-circle {\n    width: 260px;\n    height: 260px;\n  }\n  .reasons-title {\n    font-size: 28px;\n  }\n}\n\n@media (max-width: 640px) {\n  .reasons-section { padding: 70px 16px; }\n  .reasons-title { font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: -0.5px; }\n  .video-circle { width: 220px; height: 220px; }\n  .reason-circle { width: 72px; height: 72px; min-width: 72px; }\n  .reason-item { gap: 18px; padding: 26px 0; }\n  .reason-content h3 { font-size: 15px; }\n  .reason-content p { font-size: 13px; }\n}\n</style>\n\n<div class=\"reasons-section\">\n  <div class=\"reasons-container\">\n\n    <!-- GAUCHE -->\n    <div class=\"reasons-left\">\n      <div class=\"reasons-eyebrow\">Pourquoi nous choisir</div>\n      <h2 class=\"reasons-title\">5 raisons de tout abandonner pour <em>OORIGINE®</em></h2>\n      <div class=\"video-circle\">\n        <video autoplay muted loop playsinline preload=\"auto\" webkit-playsinline disableRemotePlayback x-webkit-airplay=\"deny\" disablePictureInPicture>\n          <source src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/f00fe8706e7f4c7da1b76d342a30feb5.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n        </video>\n        <img class=\"mobile-gif\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0713/6952/3289/files/4b825753ee3b4384871b6f18c99d3c2c.SD-480p-1.5Mbps-65503468-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter-2.gif?v=1771198161\" alt=\"OORIGINE colostrum en action\">\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- DROITE -->\n    <div class=\"reasons-right\">\n\n      <div class=\"reason-item\">\n        <div class=\"reason-circle\">\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0713/6952/3289/files/imgi_4_Group_1533209473_1_1.png?v=1770675698\" alt=\"Immunité\" loading=\"lazy\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"reason-content\">\n          <div class=\"reason-number\">01</div>\n          <h3>Or liquide pour une immunité forte</h3>\n          <p>Les bioactifs d'OORIGINE renforcent la barrière muqueuse et la première ligne de défense immunitaire — pour rester fort, équilibré et résilient à chaque saison.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"reason-item\">\n        <div class=\"reason-circle\">\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0713/6952/3289/files/imgi_5_span__Helps_support_hydrated_radiant-looking_skin__copy_1_1.png?v=1770675544\" alt=\"Ballonnements\" loading=\"lazy\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"reason-content\">\n          <div class=\"reason-number\">02</div>\n          <h3>Combat les ballonnements et va au-delà des probiotiques</h3>\n          <p>Prébiotiques et peptides réunis pour renforcer la paroi intestinale, nourrir le microbiome et favoriser une digestion fluide après chaque repas.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"reason-item\">\n        <div class=\"reason-circle\">\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0713/6952/3289/files/Capture_d_ecran_le_2026-02-09_a_17.31.21.png?v=1770676288\" alt=\"400 nutriments\" loading=\"lazy\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"reason-content\">\n          <div class=\"reason-number\">03</div>\n          <h3>400+ nutriments pour des bienfaits sur tout le corps</h3>\n          <p>Plus de 400 nutriments bioactifs qui renforcent vos barrières au niveau cellulaire — immunité, intestin, peau, cheveux, performance et plus encore.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"reason-item\">\n        <div class=\"reason-circle\">\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0713/6952/3289/files/imgi_7_Circle_Image_Frame_2_1.png?v=1770676302\" alt=\"Science\" loading=\"lazy\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"reason-content\">\n          <div class=\"reason-number\">04</div>\n          <h3>Alimenté par la nature, soutenu par la science</h3>\n          <p>Le carburant de performance original — vitalité sans crash de caféine ni stimulants. Validé par des milliers d'études cliniques pour des résultats que vous ressentez et voyez.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"reason-item\">\n        <div class=\"reason-circle\">\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0713/6952/3289/files/imgi_8_span__Helps_support_hydrated_radiant-looking_skin__1_1.png?v=1770675745\" alt=\"25000 clients\" loading=\"lazy\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"reason-content\">\n          <div class=\"reason-number\">05</div>\n          <h3>Plus de 25 000 clients ne peuvent plus s'en passer</h3>\n          <p>25 000+ avis 5 étoiles et plusieurs ruptures de stock le confirment — OORIGINE livre des résultats. Rejoignez le mouvement pour une vitalité globale en un seul geste.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>",
